@doctorsaluja @UniofOxford @fitterhappierAJ I dont know of any ARG-1 inhibs being trialed.

ASUNCTIS trial will show if there is benefit to Fas blockade.

There should be, but it's probably another treatment suited to early use.. not late.

@NToola9 @fitterhappierAJ A small, open-label, P2 trial of secukinumab (anti-IL-17 mAb) in hospitalized Covid-19 patients did not meet its primary endpoint, ventilator-free days at d28: 23.7 (95%CI 19.6-27.8) in group A vs. 23.8 (19.9-27.6) in group B, p=0.62

